Sphere Viewer Modifier Plug-in
==============================

The Sphere Viewer Modifier Plug-in (VMP) is an example of a Viewer Modifier
plug-in to render scene graph locations of type 'sphere' in the Viewer tab.

Environment Variables
---------------------

KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/SphereRender.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within a
   Katana resources path.
